<p>Goal Setter is an open source PHP web application developed by Lee Savage. There are a number of different implementation of this app which has been built on CakePHP, CodeIgniter, Zend Framework and a custom MVC framework.

The purpose of this is to be used as a learning tool for the different PHP web frameworks, for fun and you might even want to customise it further so that you've got your personalised goal setting app.</p>